Package: BenGood
Type: Package
Title: Assessing Goodness-of-Fit of Data to Benford's Law
Version: 0.0.0.900
Author: Mary Lesperance [aut, cre],
  Carolyn Tsao [ctb],
  Bree Wilton [ctb],
  Stanley Wong [ctb]
Maintainer: Mary Lesperance <mlespera@uvic.ca>
Description: This package provides easy-to-use tools for generating 
  simultaneous confidence intervals, running likelihood ratio tests and 
  running power tests to aid in assessing the conformance of your dataset 
  to Benford's Law.
Imports: mgcv,
          MASS
